---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Here's some information about me"
	pubDate={new Date('February 21 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		Hey there! I'm Joshua Cox, unless we're interacting online in which case I am Hibyehello. I am currently working
		to get a Bachelor's degree in Computer Engineering at Brigham Young University - Idaho. I am very passionate
		when it comes to computers. I love being able to learn new things and push the limits of my knowledge. I love to
		know how everything works and am not satisfied until I understand. One of my biggest passions has been modding
		Mario Kart Wii because it requires to be constantly learning. I also love developing desktop applications to
		help make tasks easier for the everyday person.
	</p>

</Layout>
